Pygofer (
<figureCitation id="048254F9FFE49641FE77F49E6036FF22" box="[491,622,151,177]" captionStart="FIGURE 3" captionStartId="6.[151,250,1887,1911]" captionTargetBox="[165,1426,193,1851]" captionTargetId="figure-17@6.[151,1436,181,1863]" captionTargetPageId="6" captionText="FIGURE 3. Hatigoria longistylia Tang &amp; Zhang n. sp., Holotype ♂: A. Habitus, dorsal view; B. Habitus, lateral view; C. Head, dorsal view; D. Face; E. Pygofer, lateral view; F. Pygofer, dorsal view; G. Pygofer, ventral view; H. Connective and style, ventral view; I. Aedeagus, dorsal view; J. Subgenital plate, ventral view; K. Aedeagus, lateral view. Scale bars = 1.0 mm." figureDoi="http://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5141617" httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/5141617/files/figure.png" pageId="8" pageNumber="366">Figs. 3E–G</figureCitation>
) with dorsal outer margins somewhat convex; subgenital plate (
<figureCitation id="048254F9FFE49641FAD8F49E67CBFF22" box="[1348,1427,151,177]" captionStart="FIGURE 3" captionStartId="6.[151,250,1887,1911]" captionTargetBox="[165,1426,193,1851]" captionTargetId="figure-17@6.[151,1436,181,1863]" captionTargetPageId="6" captionText="FIGURE 3. Hatigoria longistylia Tang &amp; Zhang n. sp., Holotype ♂: A. Habitus, dorsal view; B. Habitus, lateral view; C. Head, dorsal view; D. Face; E. Pygofer, lateral view; F. Pygofer, dorsal view; G. Pygofer, ventral view; H. Connective and style, ventral view; I. Aedeagus, dorsal view; J. Subgenital plate, ventral view; K. Aedeagus, lateral view. Scale bars = 1.0 mm." figureDoi="http://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5141617" httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/5141617/files/figure.png" pageId="8" pageNumber="366">Fig. 3J</figureCitation>
) nearly as long as pygofer, outer margins moderately evenly convex, apex somewhat round and nearly as broad as base; ventral appendages about as long as subgenital plate, with basal 1/2 part very broad, terminal 1/2 part slender and strongly curved mesad, with elongate spine on posterior corner; lateral margins of connective (
<figureCitation id="048254F9FFE49641FB7FF50A6761FE8E" box="[1251,1337,259,285]" captionStart="FIGURE 3" captionStartId="6.[151,250,1887,1911]" captionTargetBox="[165,1426,193,1851]" captionTargetId="figure-17@6.[151,1436,181,1863]" captionTargetPageId="6" captionText="FIGURE 3. Hatigoria longistylia Tang &amp; Zhang n. sp., Holotype ♂: A. Habitus, dorsal view; B. Habitus, lateral view; C. Head, dorsal view; D. Face; E. Pygofer, lateral view; F. Pygofer, dorsal view; G. Pygofer, ventral view; H. Connective and style, ventral view; I. Aedeagus, dorsal view; J. Subgenital plate, ventral view; K. Aedeagus, lateral view. Scale bars = 1.0 mm." figureDoi="http://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5141617" httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/5141617/files/figure.png" pageId="8" pageNumber="366">Fig. 3H</figureCitation>
) slightly vertically expanded into keeled process and touching each other medially in dorsal view, apex of vertical process broader than rest and apically acute and backward curved; style about 3.0x longer than connective, apophysis with base broad and terminus tapering, surpassing apex of connective, with about six setae at apex; aedeagal shaft (
<figureCitation id="048254F9FFE49641FAF8F566628BFE3E" captionStart="FIGURE 3" captionStartId="6.[151,250,1887,1911]" captionTargetBox="[165,1426,193,1851]" captionTargetId="figure-17@6.[151,1436,181,1863]" captionTargetPageId="6" captionText="FIGURE 3. Hatigoria longistylia Tang &amp; Zhang n. sp., Holotype ♂: A. Habitus, dorsal view; B. Habitus, lateral view; C. Head, dorsal view; D. Face; E. Pygofer, lateral view; F. Pygofer, dorsal view; G. Pygofer, ventral view; H. Connective and style, ventral view; I. Aedeagus, dorsal view; J. Subgenital plate, ventral view; K. Aedeagus, lateral view. Scale bars = 1.0 mm." figureDoi="http://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5141617" httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/5141617/files/figure.png" pageId="8" pageNumber="366">Figs. 3I, K</figureCitation>
) tubular, with a few tiny transverse wrinkles on dorsal surface, gonopore at apex.
</paragraph>
